# Simple GO Lang REST API Demo

> Simple RESTful API to create, read, update and delete records.
No database implementation yet

## Quick Start


``` bash
# Install mux router
go get -u github.com/gorilla/mux
```

``` bash
go build
./go_restapi
```

## Endpoints

### Get All Records
``` bash
GET api/records
```
### Get Single Records
``` bash
GET api/records/{id}
```

### Delete Records
``` bash
DELETE api/records/{id}
```

### Create Records
``` bash
POST api/records
```

### Update Records
``` bash
PUT api/records/{id}

```


```

